headline: Piper Sandler Maintains Overweight on Edwards Lifesciences (EW) Ahead of PARTNER 3 7-Year Results
summary: Edwards Lifesciences Corporation (NYSE:EW) ranks among the best medical device stocks to invest in. Piper Sandler maintained its Overweight rating and $90 price target for Edwards Lifesciences Corporation (NYSE:EW) on October 7, ahead of the expected 7-year findings from Edwards’ PARTNER 3 study, which is set to be presented on October 27 at the Transcatheter […]
